data.description:
Directly across the street from waterfront homes and located in the highly desirable neighborhood of Bunkers Cove. The home sits on a very large lot with great landscaping and nice patio/bbq area. 
   Inside there is an updated kitchen with 6 range gas stove and professional quality oven. All stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, and open dining area. A step down Florida room that looks out over the backyard and garden, which is ideal for cooler nights and allows for a lot of natural light into the home all year round. There are 3 large bedrooms located just off the main living room area. Master bedroom includes an updated private full bathroom. A second updated full bath located in the hallway is conveniently located for anyone in the 2 remaining rooms to use as needed. There is a 1/2 bath located just off the laundry room as well, which keeps guests  from needing to use the private rest rooms so often when entertaining and/or enjoying the holidays with family.  
   Finally, there is a detached cottage just off to the side of the home with its own separate driveway and parking area. A wonderful front porch that is ideal for early mornings listening to the birds and relaxing and beautiful sunsets in the evening over the bay. Features nearly 800 sq ft of living space including a full kitchen with bar area, living room, bedroom with new flooring throughout. As well as an updated full bathroom . This is a true detached cottage and not your typical in-law suite.
data.whatILove: A Lovely home all around, in a very peaceful and beautiful location that is both coveted and treasured by folks fortunate enough to call Bunkers Cove home.
